question:
What is the sum of the number of faces, edges and vertices of a triangular prism?

[asy]
draw((0,0)--(10,0)--(5,8.7)--cycle);
draw((0,0)--(20,20),dashed);
draw((10,0)--(30,20));
draw((5,8.7)--(25,28.7));
