answer_cot:
Denote the remaining entries by $d, e, f, g, h,$ as shown: [asy]
size(2cm);
for (int i=0; i<=3; ++i) draw((i,0)--(i,3)^^(0,i)--(3,i));
label("$x$",(0.5,2.5));label("$19$",(1.5,2.5));
